# The in-app assistant calls Gemini from the Amplify Lambda `chat-assistant`.
# No Gemini vars in `.env` for the frontend. Set the API key as a sandbox/branch secret:
#
#   npx ampx sandbox secret set GEMINI_API_KEY
#
# (Use the same sandbox identifier your team uses, e.g. `npm run backend:sandbox:hgoll`.)
# Optional: override model in amplify/functions/chat-assistant/resource.ts (GEMINI_MODEL).
